info.name: PokeTube
info.description:
To customized:
For Stylish user click the cog icon on this page, make changes, then install.

For Stylus user just install it, go to youtube click the extension and the cog icon to customized.
info.additionalInfo: tho it is suggested to use the Light Theme, you can use Dark Theme if your custom background image is darker than the text. Just be aware that Dark Theme will have issues in some part of the page.
